column3: A Hallway with nothing in it.
There is a bed in front of you. >On the bed is a small audio tape.

You find yourself in a small room with a metallic looking door. >It seems like you are located is some sort of living quarters. >In the room there is a terminal four diffrent buttons a bed and some personal belongings.
The door is in front of you. >A keypad is beside the door. >On the keypad's panel are three buttons labeled JKL.
You Pass through the door to your amazement.
A Hallway with nothing in it.
